Trading blows and brawling in the grass, two brown bear cubs go paw-to-paw in a play fight - leaving their other sibling to play the role of referee.

As the cubs fought one another in the enclosure at Hamburg's Hagenbeck Zoo, their mother had time to fish for dinner.

The scene was captured by wildlife photographer Yosuke Tani, 33, who was positioned just ten metres away from the bears. 

